            source_html+="<svg class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path d=\"M9 2a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h6a2 2 0 002-2V6.414A2 2 0 0016.414 5L14 2.586A2 2 0 0012.586 2H9z\"/><path d=\"M3 8a2 2 0 012-2v10h8a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V8z\"/></svg>"
            source_html+="${filename}</h3>"
